了。非付费用户受到的影响最大，最初每天只能看到 600 个帖子。</p><p> Threads 发布后，人们纷纷涌入，不到一周的时间，它<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/metas-threads-races-to-100-million-users-in-under-a-week-070740016.html">的用户就轻松达到了 1 亿</a>。然而，Meta 发布的 Threads 并没有提供人们期望从这样的社交网络中获得的一系列功能。该公司的高层承诺，Threads 团队正在<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/paultassi/2023/07/07/the-missing-threads-features-adam-mosseri-says-are-on-the-list/?sh=777531cb4395">开发这些功能</a>，并在过去几周内发布了<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/threads-adds-a-chronological-feed-as-twitter-burns-to-the-ground-152817251.html">按时间顺序排列的提要</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/first-big-threads-update-for-ios-helps-you-see-new-followers-195035774.html">内置翻译</a>。 Threads 的参与度较第一周的轰动一时<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/threads-users-are-already-spending-less-time-in-the-app-182738755.html">有所下降</a>，但新功能的推出可能会吸引那些早期采用者一睹为快，并成为活跃用户。 </p><div id="bc5b15eafa96465caffa352bbfa827a8"><div class="iframely-embed"><div class="iframely-responsive" style="padding-bottom:100%;"><a href="https://www.threads.net/@zuck/post/Cviggu9PdPx"></a></div></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/threads-is-getting-a-web-version-and-a-search-function-in-the-next-few-weeks-101220107.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/threads-is-getting-a-web-version-and-a-search-function-in-the-next-few-weeks-101220107.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> e52ee8e1-171b-4d70-a308-7aaf3c9905d7</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 05 Aug 2023 10:12:20 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691230332</ingested><modified> 2023-08-05T10:12:17+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></ca